    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will require a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with several large dents and peeling clear coat. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is recommended that the buyer tows the vehicle from the lot.",
